Dubai, United Arab Emirates96 contributions
Nature's beauty
Sep 2015 ‚Ä¢ Friends
The place is worth visiting. Many companies offer daily, overnight or 3 days tours with possibility to sleep on a boat or island. My friends and I chose a 2 day one night tour with the boat stay. The place is amazing but the company that organized the tour was not good at all. It is called Golden river and this is why it is bad: the food was not enough and if you ask extra, max you get is plain rice. If you want a snack you cannot get it, my friend begged for a toast and she never got it. My other friend wanted some leftover tea from the breakfast and the staff tried to charge her for this. I had the worst experience there. The entire night was impossible to sleep because the rats were running all over the roof and when i finally slept i woke up to discover my whole body is covered in bed bug bites and one of the bites was on my eyelid and i have allergic reactions to insect bites and i looked horrible. i couldn't open my eye and the staff didn't even have a first aid kid on board. In conclusion, Hanlong bay - YES! but carefully chose the boat. We paid 80 dollars but they start from 120 and negotiate it to 80, which is the real price. But ask all these questions about food and safety and hygiene.
